      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must hold ISO 9001 certification and pass regression test suite for blood-pump geometries.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 holds ISO 9001 certification; internal regression suite covering rotating-domain hemolysis benchmarks passed in full. Required level met."
    },
    {
