      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to the hemolysis transport scalar and Navier-Stokes solver; convergence order must meet theoretical expectation.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification confirmed second-order spatial convergence for both momentum and hemolysis scalar equations. Code verification complete at required level."
    },
