      "acceptanceCriteria": "Normalized index of agreement (NIA) for hemolysis index ≥ 0.85 across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "NIA computed as 0.79 across five operating points; below the 0.85 threshold. Discrepancy attributed to turbulence model limitations near blade trailing edges. Gap noted."
    },
