      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Hemolysis index (HI) as computed by the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model must be the primary QoI; secondary QoIs (shear stress, exposure time) must be documented.",
