      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection justified against hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; hemolysis power-law model constants validated against independent dataset.",
      "rationale": "SST k-ω selected with documented justification; however, hemolysis model constants taken from Giersiepen 1990 without re-calibration against modern datasets. Model form uncertainty not fully bounded."
    },
    {
